      group="Anti Legionella",
      enable=use_antLeg and weekly));
  parameter Integer trigHour=3 "Hour of the day at which control is triggered"
    annotation (Dialog(
      tab="Heat Pump Control",
      group="Anti Legionella",
      enable=use_antLeg));
